{"tid":910573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美航母「列根號」訪港　指揮官稱讓船員了解本地文化","createTime":"2018-11-21T09:26:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T09:30:13.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c88695e8915b081cc6a0009e3eb1f6e6d83d8491","tid":910573,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:26:12.000Z","msg":"美國核動力航空母艦「列根號」，聯同3艘美軍艦隻訪港，停泊在青衣對開海面，船上有美軍向附近的人揮手。<br />\n<br />\n指揮官、海軍少將Karl Thomas表示，這是他第6次訪港，形容香港是他最喜愛的太平洋港口，今次訪港主要目的是讓船員到岸上休假和了解本地文化，可以讓船員和本港市民互相接觸、增進了解，不清楚今次訪港的政治意義。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，解放軍駐港部隊司令員譚本宏昨日到船上參觀，和船員交流及觀看日常運作。艦長Pat Hannifin則表示船員將會下船參與多項活動，包括探訪學童。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1429441-20181121.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1429441-20181121.htm&d=RX7ZHns07AflqApY6FlLgbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=64854ea4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1429441-20181121.htm&h=fa90aa37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1429441-20181121.htm</a>"},{"pid":"704cd50c8ddcbd1c114d00d1b037377b71f8cb05","tid":910573,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:27:20.000Z","msg":"解放軍開放參觀 ： 讓港人了解支那"},{"pid":"b758d92c3baeb29cba043875d084eefd725634fc","tid":910573,"uid":108421,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T09:30:13.000Z","msg":"我來帶路!"}]}